java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.definitions.interactions.component.menu.StringSelectMenuDefinition.MenuOptionDefinition
Record Components:
value - the value of the select option
label - the label of the select option
description - the description of the select option
emoji - the Emoji of the select option or null
